title: Best of The Program | Guests: Bill O'Reilly & Rep. Thomas Massie | 5/1/20
description:
Joe Biden finally discussed and denied Tara Reade’s allegations that he sexually assaulted her. Surprisingly, MSNBC’s Mika Brzezinski did not go light on him in the interview. But Biden seemed afraid to release his Delaware records. Bill O’Reilly joins to discuss Biden’s karma, how bad the Democrats’ Kavanaugh standard is, and how Nancy Pelosi is even worse. Rep. Thomas Massie makes the argument for the PRIME Act to revive the local meat processing industry in the face of a shortage.
